Privacy Policy
Welcome to our application! We are committed to respecting and protecting your privacy. This privacy policy explains that the application does not collect any of your personal information, except as detailed below.
Location Services
To provide weather updates relevant to your current location, our app may require access to your device's location services. This data is only used to fetch and display weather information and is not stored or used for any other purposes. Location tracking may occur in the background even when the app is not in use, to ensure timely weather updates.
Google AdMob Advertising
The app uses Google AdMob to display advertisements. When you use this application, you may see advertisements provided by Google AdMob within the app. Google AdMob may use non-personal tracking technologies, such as ad providers and third parties, to deliver ads that match the interests and behavior of users. This information is not personally identifiable and is not linked to your personal information.
Information Security
We are committed to protecting your non-personal information through the use of modern security measures and implementing industry standards to prevent unauthorized access, misuse, or disclosure of your information.
External Links
The app may contain links to external websites or third-party services. We are not responsible for the content or privacy policies of these websites. Please check their privacy policies before using them.
Compliance with Laws
We comply with privacy and data security laws applicable in the regions where we operate.